For the 2002/03 marketing year:
(a) the minimum price referred to in Article 3 of Regulation (EC) No 2201/96 for dried plums of the "prunes d'Ente" variety shall be EUR 1935,23 per tonne net ex-producer's premises;
(b) the production aid referred to in Article 4 of that Regulation for prunes shall be EUR 671,73 per tonne net.
